<p>Right now, loot, even quest loot, comes down to rare drops on rare mobs with a /random 200.  The only way you have a chance at winning is to spend a LOT of time in one session instead of a little time in a few sessions.  Point-based systems help people with limited time earn loot progressivly instead of simply spending six hours hunting at a time and being lucky when its time to roll.</p>
