<p>I heartily agree with the sentiment, but I'm not sure we're all THAT far off. By the same calculations I gave above, a single ten-hour session in a DS expedition gets you 56 chances to get named mobs. Five two-hour sessions gets you 40. Fair? Not really. Crisis? No.</p>

